<p><strong>Currently</strong></p>

<p>I am working on Platonia, a learning-based social network based in Cambridge.</p>

<hr />

<p><strong>Also</strong></p>

<p>I am looking for participants for a meditation group and <a href="/courses/writing/intro">my writing workshop</a>.</p>

